mean_cn: prep. 不像；和……不同；  adj. 不同的
mean_en: different from a particular person or thing; used to contrast somebody/something with another person or thing; not typical of somebody/something
sentence: One of these men is unlike the others.
sentence_trans: 这些男人中，有一个和其他人不同。
word_etyma: un不 + like像 → unlike与……不像、不同
